    public class HistoryActivity
extends androidx.fragment.app.Fragment
    this HistoryActivity is a java class which extends fragment and this class will fetch data from sqlite database and using these data a single record is created then these records will be stored as ListArray as RecordList. Created RecordList will be showed to user.
